cs.HC, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.MM

The paper focuses on the security and memorability of free-form multitouch gestures for mobile authentication, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The study also involves collecting and analyzing data (cs.CY), implementing a recognizer (cs.SI), and evaluating performance (cs.MM). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
